THEY JUST WON'T LEAVE.

38:00.570 --> 38:02.948
YOU ASKED TO SPEAK WITH ME,

38:00.570 --> 38:02.948
MR. FORD,

38:02.948 --> 38:04.449
SO LET'S SPEAK.

38:04.449 --> 38:06.076
WE RECOVERED THE $50 MILLION

38:06.076 --> 38:08.120
FROM ERICKSON'S BANK

38:06.076 --> 38:08.120
IN THE CAYMANS.

38:08.120 --> 38:09.579
I WOULD LIKE TO DISTRIBUTE

38:08.120 --> 38:09.579
THAT MONEY

38:09.579 --> 38:10.830
TO THE PEOPLE HE STOLE IT FROM.

38:10.830 --> 38:13.917
I HAVE NO CLAIM ON THAT MONEY.

38:13.917 --> 38:16.044
AND I DON'T BELIEVE

38:13.917 --> 38:16.044
I WISH TO PICK A FIGHT

38:16.044 --> 38:17.712
WITH A MAN

38:16.044 --> 38:17.712
SUCH AS YOURSELF...

38:17.712 --> 38:18.880
IF I CAN AVOID IT.

38:20.215 --> 38:21.591
WHAT ABOUT THE MARSHAL?

38:21.591 --> 38:23.135
I'LL TAKE CARE OF HER.

38:23.135 --> 38:25.637
WELCOME TO CANADA.

38:25.637 --> 38:27.346
PLEASE HAVE

38:25.637 --> 38:27.346
YOUR PASSPORT OR NEXUS CARD

38:27.346 --> 38:29.766
OUT AND AVAILABLE

38:27.346 --> 38:29.766
FOR INSPECTION.

38:29.766 --> 38:31.350
JUST A LITTLE WEEKEND GETAWAY.

38:31.350 --> 38:33.394
YOU MUST PROVIDE RECEIPTS

38:31.350 --> 38:33.394
FOR ANY PURCHASES MADE

38:33.394 --> 38:34.896
OUT OF COUNTRY.

38:34.896 --> 38:36.106
THANK YOU.

38:36.106 --> 38:37.607
HOLD IT THERE, MARSHAL.

38:46.491 --> 38:49.786
[ SIGHS ]

38:49.786 --> 38:52.914
THERE IS ONE OTHER THING

38:49.786 --> 38:52.914
I'D LIKE TO ASK OF YOU,

38:52.914 --> 38:56.042
AND THAT IS THAT YOU

38:52.914 --> 38:56.042
OR ANY OF YOUR ASSOCIATES

38:56.042 --> 38:58.962
LEAVE ERICKSON ALONE IN PRISON.

38:58.962 --> 39:00.130
OUT OF THE QUESTION.

39:00.130 --> 39:01.506
I NEED ERICKSON DEAD.

39:01.506 --> 39:02.715
WELL, NO.

39:02.715 --> 39:04.509
NO, YOU JUST NEED HIM

39:02.715 --> 39:04.509
QUIET, REALLY.

39:04.509 --> 39:06.886
HE WAS PICKED UP BY THE POLICE.

39:06.886 --> 39:08.346
HIS MARSHAL'S GONE ROGUE.

39:08.346 --> 39:11.099
HE'S LOSING HIS IMMUNITY

39:08.346 --> 39:11.099
AS WE SPEAK.

39:11.099 --> 39:13.685
HE'S GONNA STAND TRIAL

39:11.099 --> 39:13.685
FOR HIS FINANCIAL INFRACTIONS

39:13.685 --> 39:15.645
AND GO TO JAIL

39:13.685 --> 39:15.645
FOR A VERY LONG TIME.

39:15.645 --> 39:18.190
LET HIM LIVE AND ENJOY IT.

39:21.776 --> 39:24.403
YOU KNOW, MY ORGANIZATION,

39:21.776 --> 39:24.403
IN ITS ORIGINAL AND PUREST FORM,

39:24.403 --> 39:26.656
WAS LAW ENFORCEMENT.

39:27.699 --> 39:29.450
NEIGHBORHOODS WHERE

39:27.699 --> 39:29.450
THE POLICE DIDN'T HAVE

39:29.450 --> 39:30.702
THE ABILITY TO ENFORCE THE LAW.

39:30.702 --> 39:31.703
MM.

39:31.703 --> 39:33.288
THERE WAS A PURPOSE.

39:33.288 --> 39:35.414
THEY WERE TRYING

39:33.288 --> 39:35.414
TO BUILD SOMETHING.

39:35.414 --> 39:38.293
WE LOST SIGHT OF THAT.

39:40.795 --> 39:43.840
WELL, WE CAN ALL BE BETTER, HUH?

39:49.428 --> 39:52.265
GONNA BE HARD WORK GETTING THAT

39:49.428 --> 39:52.265
LANDSCAPING BUSINESS UP AGAIN?

39:52.265 --> 39:54.684
THE THING I'VE LEARNED

39:52.265 --> 39:54.684
ABOUT HARD WORK, MR. FORD --

39:54.684 --> 39:57.187
MAKES COMING HOME AT NIGHT

39:54.684 --> 39:57.187
TO THE PEOPLE THAT LOVE YOU

39:57.187 --> 39:58.730
FEEL EVEN BETTER.

39:58.730 --> 40:01.733
THAT'S TRUE.

39:58.730 --> 40:01.733
HEY, TAKE CARE.

40:04.110 --> 40:05.237
[ SIGHS ]

40:08.907 --> 40:10.116
OH, HEY. THE CAR?

40:10.116 --> 40:11.450
BACK WHERE WE FOUND IT.

40:11.450 --> 40:12.493
OH, GOOD.

40:12.493 --> 40:14.079
THE OWNER'S GONNA BE BACK SOON.

40:14.079 --> 40:17.207
NOW, LET ME JUST ROLL THIS BACK

40:14.079 --> 40:17.207
FOR A SECOND, NATE.

40:17.207 --> 40:20.459
YOU KNEW THAT THAT MUSSOLINI CAR

40:17.207 --> 40:20.459
WOULD DRIVE ERICKSON CRAZY.

40:20.459 --> 40:22.712
SO CRAZY THAT HE WOULD CALL

40:20.459 --> 40:22.712
HIS OLD CAR CONTACT,

40:22.712 --> 40:25.298
ACCESS SECRET BANK ACCOUNTS,

40:22.712 --> 40:25.298
TURN ON HIS MARSHAL BABYSITTER,

40:25.298 --> 40:27.008
AND ALMOST GET TAKEN OUT

40:25.298 --> 40:27.008
BY THE MOB GUYS

40:27.008 --> 40:28.718
THAT HE PLANNED

40:27.008 --> 40:28.718
TO TESTIFY AGAINST?

40:28.718 --> 40:29.969
MM-HMM.

40:29.969 --> 40:31.346
THAT'S LIKE

40:29.969 --> 40:31.346
FIVE DIFFERENT THINGS

40:31.346 --> 40:32.722
NOBODY COULD HAVE KNOWN

40:31.346 --> 40:32.722
WOULD HAPPEN.

40:32.722 --> 40:34.266
I ONLY KNEW THREE OF THE FIVE.

40:34.266 --> 40:36.184
AH. I KNEW IT.

40:34.266 --> 40:36.184
SEE, WHICH THREE?

40:38.228 --> 40:39.729
OH, COME ON, NATE, DON'T --

40:39.729 --> 40:41.106
DON'T DO ME LIKE THAT, NATE.

40:41.231 --> 40:43.775
DON'T DO ME LIKE THAT, NATE.

40:47.153 --> 40:50.365
I COULDN'T HELP OVERHEARING

40:47.153 --> 40:50.365
WHAT YOU SAID IN THE WAREHOUSE

40:50.365 --> 40:52.200
ABOUT PUTTING THE PAST

40:50.365 --> 40:52.200
BEHIND YOU.

40:52.200 --> 40:55.203
I HAD A GUN TO MY HEAD.

40:55.203 --> 40:56.495
THIS IS OUR BAR.

40:56.495 --> 40:59.082
I'M SURE I CAN RUSTLE UP A GUN

40:56.495 --> 40:59.082
SOMEWHERE.

40:59.082 --> 41:00.333
MM.

41:00.333 --> 41:02.168
-YOU WERE WRONG ABOUT ONE THING.

41:00.333 --> 41:02.168
-REALLY?

41:02.168 --> 41:04.879
BECAUSE I COULDN'T POSSIBLY

41:02.168 --> 41:04.879
BE RIGHT, COULD I?

41:04.879 --> 41:08.716
WANTING TO MOVE ON

41:04.879 --> 41:08.716
WITH OR WITHOUT YOU --

41:08.716 --> 41:10.218
IT MATTERS.

41:10.218 --> 41:12.595
WE MATTER.
